<window>
	<vlayout>
		1. The simplest use is to specify it with self as follows. Then, the anchor is disabled when it is clicked.
		<a label="OK" autodisable="self" />
		<div>
			2. The following disables both anchors, when one of them is clicked.
			<a id="ok" label="OK 2" autodisable="ok,cancel" />
			<a id="cancel" label="Cancel" autodisable="ok,cancel" />
		</div>
		3. Change the disable status.
		<button label="Change OK 2 to disabled" onClick='ok.setDisabled(true)'/>
		<button label="Change OK 2 to enabled" onClick='ok.setDisabled(false)'/>
	</vlayout>
</window>
